title: 25 - Life with God {Finale}
description:
What does it look like to follow God as we are re-entering life post-COVID? This has been an incredible season talking about deep, hard things and we hope it has encouraged you like it has encouraged us. THANK YOU for being part of the Made for This family!

Sign up for emails, it's how we hear from you! Go to jennieallen.com
